flowchart LR
  Merchant[Merchant Dashboard] --> Radius[Local Reach Radius]
  Merchant --> Rules[Campaign Guardrails]
  Merchant --> EventRefresh[Refresh Local Events]
  Merchant --> Spark[Ask Spark Recommendation]

  EventRefresh --> EventAdapter[Local Event Adapter]
  EventAdapter --> Events[Upcoming Event Evidence + Source Links]

  Radius --> Context[Local Business Context]
  Rules --> Context
  Events --> Context
  Places[Google Places Signals] --> Context
  Analytics[Aggregate Performance] --> Context

  Context --> Recommendation[Spark Recommendation]
  Recommendation --> Apply[Apply Suggested Settings]
  Apply --> UpdatedRules[Updated Campaign Settings]
  UpdatedRules --> OfferEngine[Generated Offer Engine]
  OfferEngine --> Campaign[Active Generated Campaign]
  Campaign --> Analytics
